title: Justin Timberlake in 'Palmer' Is Actually Pretty Good
description:
Liz Kelly, Kate Halliwell, and Amelia Wedemeyer talk about 'Palmer,' the tear-jerking movie starring Justin Timberlake that may or may not relaunch his acting career.
